title: Donald Trump at 32 percent support in new poll on 2016 GOP field
text: Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump has the support of nearly one-third of Republicans and GOP-leaning independents, according to a new poll that shows an even greater percentage of voters say he's the candidate most likely to win the party's nomination and the candidate most likely to win in the general ... ...
